org.apache.flink.graph

类 IterationConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.graph.IterationConfiguration
  • 直接已知子类:
    GSAConfiguration, ScatterGatherConfiguration, VertexCentricConfiguration

    public abstract class IterationConfiguration
extends Object
    This is used as a base class for vertex-centric iteration or gather-sum-apply iteration configuration.

        public int getParallelism()
        Gets the iteration's parallelism.

      • setSolutionSetUnmanagedMemory

        public void setSolutionSetUnmanagedMemory(boolean unmanaged)
        Defines whether the solution set is kept in managed memory (Flink's internal way of keeping object in serialized form) or as a simple object map. By default, the solution set runs in managed memory.
        参数:
        unmanaged - True, to keep the solution set in unmanaged memory, false otherwise.

      • isSolutionSetUnmanagedMemory

        public boolean isSolutionSetUnmanagedMemory()
        Gets whether the solution set is kept in managed memory (Flink's internal way of keeping object in serialized form) or as a simple object map. By default, the solution set runs in managed memory.
        返回:
        True, if the solution set is in unmanaged memory, false otherwise.

      • isOptNumVertices

        public boolean isOptNumVertices()
        Gets whether the number of vertices option is set. By default, the number of vertices option is not set.
        返回:
        True, if the number of vertices option is set, false otherwise.

      • setOptNumVertices

        public void setOptNumVertices(boolean optNumVertices)
        Sets the number of vertices option. By default, the number of vertices option is not set.
        参数:
        optNumVertices - True, to set this option, false otherwise.

      • registerAggregator

        public void registerAggregator(String name,
                               org.apache.flink.api.common.aggregators.Aggregator<?> aggregator)
        Registers a new aggregator. Aggregators registered here are available during the execution of the vertex updates via GatherFunction.getIterationAggregator(String) and GatherFunction.getPreviousIterationAggregate(String).
        参数:
        name - The name of the aggregator, used to retrieve it and its aggregates during execution.
        aggregator - The aggregator.

      • getAggregators

        public Map<String,org.apache.flink.api.common.aggregators.Aggregator<?>> getAggregators()
        Gets the set of aggregators that are registered for this vertex-centric iteration.
        返回:
        a Map of the registered aggregators, where the key is the aggregator name and the value is the Aggregator object
